Text: This’s all I do. I just listen to obesity podcasts and watch obesity pandemic docs.  It’s weird but I feel like I’m an obese person who won’t learn even though I’m not obese.   It’s strange, i guess I’m part of the problem until I have a six pack lol. I just love male body standards :...)
